{"tid":1382231,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"前綫必須科學常識: 如何分辨風向","createTime":"2019-07-29T12:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T19:50:48.000Z","uid":276716,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d764482f9306f3b646398a8b65f098c99f5cd6a8","tid":1382231,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:10:33.000Z","msg":"最近好多手足留意風向問題，我就講下同風向有關嘅基本常識。<br />\n<br />\n上風、下風<br />\n首先要分別上風upwind 、下風downwind。下圖清楚睇到，氣體會由上風位置流向下風位置，所以緊記上風係有利位置。對陣時儘量選擇上風位(即係逆風而行)！退守、前進、集結都儘量向上風位！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RqWNV3v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRqWNV3v.png&h=8c700592&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如何分辨風向<br />\n初級: 留意任何隨風飄動嘅物件，例如旗幟、樹枝、晾衫、頭髮。<br />\n網上可以揾到簡易風向儀嘅製作方法。不過我建議最簡單方式，就係黐一條幼綿繩喺遮頭，舉起把遮，觀察綿繩擺動就可以知道風向。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0EPPpXx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0EPPpXx.jpg&h=5a79b92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n進階: 有經驗嘅人，例如帆船舵手，係可以用臉頰感受風向。一般人都可以練習到呢個技巧。首先企定，頭左右擰，直至感受到風由正面吹落自己塊面，或聽到耳邊有呼呼聲，咁呢個就係風吹嚟嘅方向，你向前行就係行向上風位置。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.wikihow.com/Determine-Wind-Direction\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.wikihow.com%2FDetermine-Wind-Direction&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiRjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=9dca8d68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.wikihow.com/Determine-Wind-Direction</a><br />\n<br />\n諗到再講。"},{"pid":"138eb4d6137304ae4863ff0d07f95abf57a15f76","tid":1382231,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:40:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e706cf28568213ebc371458634239ff46c5701cf","tid":1382231,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:26:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"07f5fa85f4cb109d80ddafacf8c87a50fee92628","tid":1382231,"uid":194298,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:32:50.000Z","msg":"我有個方法仲簡單<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AOXENE8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAOXENE8.png&h=b15e4e13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開天文台app就睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圓點係箭頭，尾巴代表風速，愈多尾風速愈高"},{"pid":"f3580f69dfc84c84ac25f1db9915cbcb033a9c59","tid":1382231,"uid":276716,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"07f5fa85f4cb109d80ddafacf8c87a50fee92628","tid":1382231,"uid":194298,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:32:50.000Z","msg":"我有個方法仲簡單<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AOXENE8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAOXENE8.png&h=b15e4e13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開天文台app就睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圓點係箭頭，尾巴代表風速，愈多尾風速愈高"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:36:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個要注意風向會隨地形變化，尤其係市區樓宇之間嘅流動會有好大變化，可以同海邊/高地完全唔同"},{"pid":"eae339a6024f4d9397c15175e30639f85141327f","tid":1382231,"uid":260325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:43:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91b5cbbd105859e62a5605828ea78a05287ed2a3","tid":1382231,"uid":65210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d764482f9306f3b646398a8b65f098c99f5cd6a8","tid":1382231,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:10:33.000Z","msg":"最近好多手足留意風向問題，我就講下同風向有關嘅基本常識。<br />\n<br />\n上風、下風<br />\n首先要分別上風upwind 、下風downwind。下圖清楚睇到，氣體會由上風位置流向下風位置，所以緊記上風係有利位置。對陣時儘量選擇上風位(即係逆風而行)！退守、前進、集結都儘量向上風位！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RqWNV3v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRqWNV3v.png&h=8c700592&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如何分辨風向<br />\n初級: 留意任何隨風飄動嘅物件，例如旗幟、樹枝、晾衫、頭髮。<br />\n網上可以揾到簡易風向儀嘅製作方法。不過我建議最簡單方式，就係黐一條幼綿繩喺遮頭，舉起把遮，觀察綿繩擺動就可以知道風向。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0EPPpXx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0EPPpXx.jpg&h=5a79b92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n進階: 有經驗嘅人，例如帆船舵手，係可以用臉頰感受風向。一般人都可以練習到呢個技巧。首先企定，頭左右擰，直至感受到風由正面吹落自己塊面，或聽到耳邊有呼呼聲，咁呢個就係風吹嚟嘅方向，你向前行就係行向上風位置。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.wikihow.com/Determine-Wind-Direction\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.wikihow.com%2FDetermine-Wind-Direction&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiRjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=9dca8d68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.wikihow.com/Determine-Wind-Direction</a><br />\n<br />\n諗到再講。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:54:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3decc88ed251bf9f1227978419159dc8494315f4","tid":1382231,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91b5cbbd105859e62a5605828ea78a05287ed2a3","tid":1382231,"uid":65210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d764482f9306f3b646398a8b65f098c99f5cd6a8","tid":1382231,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:10:33.000Z","msg":"最近好多手足留意風向問題，我就講下同風向有關嘅基本常識。<br />\n<br />\n上風、下風<br />\n首先要分別上風upwind 、下風downwind。下圖清楚睇到，氣體會由上風位置流向下風位置，所以緊記上風係有利位置。對陣時儘量選擇上風位(即係逆風而行)！退守、前進、集結都儘量向上風位！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RqWNV3v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRqWNV3v.png&h=8c700592&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如何分辨風向<br />\n初級: 留意任何隨風飄動嘅物件，例如旗幟、樹枝、晾衫、頭髮。<br />\n網上可以揾到簡易風向儀嘅製作方法。不過我建議最簡單方式，就係黐一條幼綿繩喺遮頭，舉起把遮，觀察綿繩擺動就可以知道風向。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0EPPpXx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0EPPpXx.jpg&h=5a79b92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br 