驗嘅人，例如帆船舵手，係可以用臉頰感受風向。一般人都可以練習到呢個技巧。首先企定，頭左右擰，直至感受到風由正面吹落自己塊面，或聽到耳邊有呼呼聲，咁呢個就係風吹嚟嘅方向，你向前行就係行向上風位置。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.wikihow.com/Determine-Wind-Direction\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.wikihow.com%2FDetermine-Wind-Direction&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiRjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=9dca8d68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.wikihow.com/Determine-Wind-Direction</a><br />\n<br />\n諗到再講。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:54:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:17:38.000Z","msg":"可以點update?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:18:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee2e7f8bceb07c03c4d3a6e3d284ede8eff2dae7","tid":1382231,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:45:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"80c518f3c3b6c3b3041245d575d9fd46da038b4d","tid":1382231,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:40:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6c9e8f6d5d0fa315d40b93352fd00a713c33aad0","tid":1382231,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:25:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"09f972cb5f3f21679303a13e92878260cef294bf","tid":1382231,"uid":138740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:14:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"13b17acbe58e83fb27040c92d4370d113577d0b8","tid":1382231,"uid":295218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d764482f9306f3b646398a8b65f098c99f5cd6a8","tid":1382231,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:10:33.000Z","msg":"最近好多手足留意風向問題，我就講下同風向有關嘅基本常識。<br />\n<br />\n上風、下風<br />\n首先要分別上風upwind 、下風downwind。下圖清楚睇到，氣體會由上風位置流向下風位置，所以緊記上風係有利位置。對陣時儘量選擇上風位(即係逆風而行)！退守、前進、集結都儘量向上風位！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RqWNV3v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRqWNV3v.png&h=8c700592&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如何分辨風向<br />\n初級: 留意任何隨風飄動嘅物件，例如旗幟、樹枝、晾衫、頭髮。<br />\n網上可以揾到簡易風向儀嘅製作方法。不過我建議最簡單方式，就係黐一條幼綿繩喺遮頭，舉起把遮，觀察綿繩擺動就可以知道風向。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0EPPpXx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0EPPpXx.jpg&h=5a79b92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n進階: 有經驗嘅人，例如帆船舵手，係可以用臉頰感受風向。一般人都可以練習到呢個技巧。首先企定，頭左右擰，直至感受到風由正面吹落自己塊面，或聽到耳邊有呼呼聲，咁呢個就係風吹嚟嘅方向，你向前行就係行向上風位置。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.wikihow.com/Determine-Wind-Direction\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.wikihow.com%2FDetermine-Wind-Direction&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiRjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=9dca8d68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.wikihow.com/Determine-Wind-Direction</a><br />\n<br />\n諗到再講。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:27:43.000Z","msg":"但前線無物資，一人一個豬咀同眼罩，仲會怕？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[請廣傳]幫幫最前線嘅朋友<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1392311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1392311</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n懶人包<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/inkstonenews/videos/1120804801452822?s=100000869193442&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Finkstonenews%2Fvideos%2F1120804801452822%3Fs%3D100000869193442%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiRjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=3346584a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/inkstonenews/videos/1120804801452822?s=100000869193442&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"a6130605fb6ae29af3249bb7843578f266413c82","tid":1382231,"uid":106480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T19:34:06.000Z","msg":"辨風向好重要，推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oSoQgnF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https:/